{"tid":1183927,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為供應商率先捱不住 員工被迫放3個月假","createTime":"2019-06-03T09:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T13:07:46.000Z","uid":28114,"like":105,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"01083aa5cda8857968ff41c5af6963c145dd56d5","tid":1183927,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190603/large/1559540158_53a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190603%2Flarge%2F1559540158_53a8.jpg&h=64929277&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譽銘新精密廠房。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190603/large/1559539987_e346.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190603%2Flarge%2F1559539987_e346.jpg&h=93894224&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上流出華為供應商譽銘新精密通告。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n華為遭美國頒下禁令，有供應商終捱不住，宣佈讓員工「分批放假」。日前網上流出華為供應商東莞市譽銘新精密通告，明言受中美貿易戰影響，訂單減少，員工「依法分批放假」，最長不超過6個月，先按3個月分批放假。<br />\n<br />\n通告指貿易戰令公司業務嚴重受影響，望員工配合放假措拖，共度時艱。放假首月將按法律支付正常工作時間工資，第2個月起付東莞最低工資80%作生活補助金，並囑付員工放假期間切勿進入生產區域。據悉譽銘新精密有8000多名員工，未知受影響員工人數。<br />\n<br />\n記者嘗試聯絡譽銘新精密，惟電話未能接通。<br />\n<br />\n據譽銘網站介紹，該公司2011年成立，從事精密模具製造、CNC加工等，客戶包括華為、中興、聯想、OPPO、魅族等。公司年產值可逾30億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190603/59671318\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190603%2F59671318&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOFIIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=1bf512ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190603%2F59671318&h=4e04a01f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190603/59671318</a>"},{"pid":"17cb5645d908ec32602baf2cdc26b9a8f8eeacf1","tid":1183927,"uid":52194,"like":86,"dislike":0,"score":86,"c